headline: 3 Reasons Investors Watch ResMed (RMD)
summary: ResMed has had an impressive run over the past six months as its shares have beaten the S&P 500 by 11.9%. The stock now trades at $281.96, marking a 20.7% gain. This was partly due to its solid quarterly results, and the run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
